data.description: A beautifully maintained property with exceptional curb appeal. The interior boasts high ceilings, a built-in entertainment center, and abundant natural light. The kitchen features a large island, granite countertops, and a built-in appliances, along with massive walk-in pantry. The expansive master bedroom offers a bathroom with a jetted tub, walk-in shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Additional highlights include a laundry rom with storage cabinets and sink, 2 separate A/C units, a separate entrance casita with a kitchenette and bathroom, a 3-car garage with plenty of cabinet storage, a covered patio, and stunning mountain views. Solar panels are paid for! This property is fully fenced and landscaped with no HOA fees. Close to Kayenta Art village, hiking, trails, reservoirs & more!
